name: CALLIGRAPHY #6 - Get some.
description: Writing gives the mind discipline. I use notes like these to rein in the mind. Notes serve as psychological parameters in which I allow mind to operate. Because without that structure, it is liable to go rogue into thought streams I otherwise wouldn’t prefer to spend my time on. Notes make the infinite mindspace much easier to handle; it allows the mind to focus on what is pertinent. “Get some” is such a note used to focus on creation and proaction.
